OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776942175
OL,3,CMan dumped 50 dead hares and two rare
OL,4,Cbirds in 'horror movie scene', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA man dumped the bodies of 50 hares
OL,8,Foutside a village shop before smearing
OL,9,Fthe blood of one across the store
OL,10,Ffront and stuffing a dead kestrel and
OL,11,Fa barn owl under the door handles in a
OL,12,F"horror movie scene", a court has
OL,13,Fheard.
OL,15,FJames Kempster, 39, of Totton in
OL,16,FSouthampton, is on trial at
OL,17,FSouthampton Magistrates' Court charged
OL,18,Fwith two counts of possessing a dead
OL,19,Fbird under the Wildlife and
OL,20,FCountryside Act and a charge of
OL,21,Fcriminal damage to the shop front.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
