PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776942175
OL,3,CMan dumped 50 dead hares and two rare
OL,4,Cbirds in 'horror movie scene', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe court heard the alleged incident
OL,8,Fwas caught on CCTV outside Broughton
OL,9,FCommunity Shop in the early hours of
OL,10,F15 March 2024.
OL,12,FAdam Cooper, prosecuting, said: "This
OL,13,Fis a horror movie scene outside a
OL,14,FBroughton village shop, it's a small
OL,15,FHampshire village.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776942175
OL,3,CMan dumped 50 dead hares and two rare
OL,4,Cbirds in 'horror movie scene', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"In the middle of the night, at
OL,8,F3.23am, three men arrived outside the
OL,9,Fshop by car, the driver remains in the
OL,10,Fcar, having manoeuvred it to a
OL,11,Fposition so the boot is adjacent to
OL,12,Fthe forecourt, two men get out.
OL,14,F"They are both dressed in tracksuits,
OL,15,Fhoods up, balaclavas covering their
OL,16,Ffaces so neither can be identified.
OL,18,F"They get out to discard the bodies of
OL,19,F50 dead hares over the forecourt,
OL,20,Fstrewn about deliberately to maximise
OL,21,Ftheir coverage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776942175
OL,3,CMan dumped 50 dead hares and two rare
OL,4,Cbirds in 'horror movie scene', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"The Crown says one of those two men
OL,8,Fis James Kempster."
OL,10,FThe prosecutor said DNA discovered on
OL,11,Fthe dead birds was matched to the
OL,12,Fdefendant who was also linked to the
OL,13,Fincident through his mobile phone
OL,14,Flocation, his clothing and connections
OL,15,Fto the car which was found burned out
OL,16,Fin a country lane.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
