PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776942175
OL,3,CMan dumped 50 dead hares and two rare
OL,4,Cbirds in 'horror movie scene', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe added that the motive for the
OL,8,Fincident was unknown and said: "To
OL,9,Ffind him guilty we do not need to know
OL,10,Fwhy and it may be that we do not get
OL,11,Fto understand why."
OL,13,FKempster denies the charges and the
OL,14,Ftrial continues.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
